Jagajaga is Indonesia application for mobile device security, which is developed by Wolu, and powered by Zimperium’s engine, a global leader and world proven advanced mobile security solution.

Zimperium Awards
> Cybersecurity Excellence Awards 2020: Best Product Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning
> 2019 Banking CIO Outlook's Top 10 Mobile Banking Solution Providers in APAC

Jagajaga is a focused and advanced app used by professionals, bankers, engineers and online shoppers, which is simple and NOT collect your Personal Identity to secure your device from WiFi, Virus and Phishing Site attacks.

*** Scan and Detect ***
- Auto-scan Files and Apps, show Safe or NOT Safe
- Detect the harmful website and BLOCK it
- Monitor your WiFi network and Detect suspicious activity in the real-time

*** Protect Your Data ***
- Drag and Drop your Files and PRIVATE photos into the Secure Storage
- Notify you and Alert you if you have “NOT Secure” settings
- Additional Passcode lock for the APPs on the device

*** Privacy ***
- Your Privacy is our TOP and CORE value, App never see your message, photos, videos, etc
- Passcode is kept by you, once your locked the file, No one can open it
